Jordan M. PAGLIA, Plaintiff-Appellee/Cross-Appellant,
v.
Heather A. TAYLOR, Defendant-Appellant/Cross-Appellee. No. 18-1387 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The parties appeal the district court order establishing paternity, custody, visitation, and support of their child. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED AND REMANDED.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED. REMANDED.
